OL,7,FThe family of an RUC officer killed in
OL,8,Fthe Chinook helicopter disaster have
OL,9,Fspoken out for the first time in an
OL,10,Fappeal for answers.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Dennis
OL,13,FBunting was one of 29 people who died
OL,14,Fwhen the helicopter crashed into
OL,15,FScotland's Mull of Kintyre in 1994.
OL,17,F"I knew he didn't want to get on that
OL,18,Fflight," his wife Lynn Bunting said.
