OL,7,F"I knew he didn't want to get on it.
OL,8,FTo just see all that burned grass and
OL,9,Fyou know, the whole of the hillside
OL,10,Fwas just a complete mess, and I still
OL,11,Fcan't believe it."
OL,13,FFor 31 years, Lynn Bunting has been
OL,14,Fliving with the loss of her husband.
OL,15,FShe was plunged into grief when a
OL,16,FChinook helicopter came down over
OL,17,FScotland's Mull of Kintyre.
OL,19,FRUC officer Dennis Bunting was one of
OL,20,F29 on board who stood no chance of
OL,21,Fsurvival.
