OL,7,FHis daughter Shannon was only four
OL,8,Fyears old at the time.
OL,10,F"It's been like a huge gap for sure,"
OL,11,Fshe said. "You know, although we've
OL,12,Fkept his memory alive, I'm devastated
OL,13,Fthat I like that I didn't get to know
OL,14,Fhim, that I didn't know him as an
OL,15,Fadult, that I don't have him here."
OL,17,FIt's a grief compounded by a lack of
OL,18,Fanswers.
