OL,7,FTwo special forces pilots were first
OL,8,Fblamed for the disaster, later had
OL,9,Ftheir names were cleared.
OL,11,FNow it has emerged there were serious
OL,12,Fsafety concerns surrounding the
OL,13,FChinook helicopter used, but files
OL,14,Frelating to the crash have been sealed
OL,15,Ffor 100 years.
