OL,7,F"What could possibly be in those
OL,8,Fdocuments that can't be useful to help
OL,9,Fprevent this again, that can't be
OL,10,Fhelpful for all of these families to
OL,11,Fbe able to lay the memory of their
OL,12,Floved ones to rest," Shannon Bunting
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FFamilies are demanding a judge-led
OL,16,Fpublic inquiry have been to Downing
OL,17,FStreet and recently met with ministers
OL,18,Ffrom the Ministry of Defense.
