OL,7,FIn a statement, the MOD says its focus
OL,8,Fis on responding to claims made by the
OL,9,FChinook Justice Campaign, but say they
OL,10,Funderstand that the lack of certainty
OL,11,Fabout the cause of the crash has added
OL,12,Fto the distress of families.
OL,14,FLynn Bunting said: "For him to die in
OL,15,Fthose situations when I thought he was
OL,16,Fgoing to be lucky enough to get to
OL,17,Fpeace - and he didn't make it, and it
OL,18,Fwasn't the Troubles that killed him."
